---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Story — Mamma Gwenny's Authentic Caribbean Seasonings"
  description="Discover the story behind Mamma Gwenny's — authentic Caribbean seasonings handcrafted with love, using recipes passed down through generations."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero" style="padding-top: 9rem;">
    <div class="about-hero__pattern"></div>
    <div class="container about-hero__inner">
      <h1>Our Story</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__subtitle">The heart behind the flavour</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story content -->
  <section class="about-content section">
    <div class="container about-content__inner">
      <div class="about-content__text">
        <h2>A Taste of the Caribbean, Made with Love</h2>
        <p>
          Mamma Gwenny's story begins in the kitchen — where the rich aromas of Caribbean spices
          filled the air and every meal was prepared with care, tradition, and a whole lot of love.
          For generations, our family recipes have brought people together around the table, creating
          moments of joy and connection through food.
        </p>
        <p>
          What started as a cherished family tradition soon became something bigger. Friends,
          neighbours, and community members couldn't get enough of Mamma Gwenny's signature
          seasoning blends. The secret? Authentic Caribbean recipes, the finest ingredients, and
          a dedication to doing things the right way — by hand, with heart.
        </p>

        <h2>Handcrafted, Never Mass-Produced</h2>
        <p>
          Every jar of Mamma Gwenny's seasoning is mixed by hand in small batches. We believe that
          great flavour can't be rushed or replicated by machines. Each blend is carefully crafted
          to capture the true essence of Caribbean cooking — bold, vibrant, and full of warmth.
        </p>
        <p>
          From our Fish Flavour Seasoning that brings the taste of the islands to your Friday
          night dinner, to our fiery Jerk Seasoning that's perfect for summer barbecues — every
          product in our range has been developed with authenticity at its core.
        </p>

        <h2>From Our Kitchen to Yours</h2>
        <p>
          Today, Mamma Gwenny's seasonings are enjoyed by food lovers across Europe. But no
          matter how far our spices travel, the heart of what we do stays the same: sharing
          authentic Caribbean flavour with the world, one meal at a time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're a seasoned Caribbean cook or trying these flavours for the first time,
          we're here to help you create something special. Because at Mamma Gwenny's, we believe
          that the best meals are made with love — and a great seasoning.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-content__sidebar">
        <div class="about-values">
          <div class="about-value">
            <span class="about-value__icon">🌿</span>
            <h3 class="about-value__title">Natural Ingredients</h3>
            <p>Only the finest herbs and spices, carefully sourced for authentic Caribbean flavour.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-value">
            <span class="about-value__icon">🤲</span>
            <h3 class="about-value__title">Handmade</h3>
            <p>Every batch is mixed by hand in small quantities to ensure quality and consistency.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-value">
            <span class="about-value__icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span>
            <h3 class="about-value__title">Family Recipes</h3>
            <p>Authentic recipes passed down through generations of Caribbean cooking tradition.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-value">
            <span class="about-value__icon">🌍</span>
            <h3 class="about-value__title">Europe-Wide</h3>
            <p>Delivering authentic Caribbean flavour to kitchens across Europe.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta section bg-pattern">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="about-cta__heading">Ready to Taste the Caribbean?</h2>
      <p class="about-cta__text">Explore our range of authentic handcrafted seasonings.</p>
      <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Shop Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
    padding-block: var(--space-8);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero__pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/patterns/tropical-pattern.png');
    background-size: 400px;
    background-repeat: repeat;
    opacity: 0.08;
  }

  .about-hero__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about-hero__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-script);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Content */
  .about-content__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-9);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-content__text h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-on-surface);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-7);
  }

  .about-content__text h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-content__text p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Sidebar values */
  .about-values {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    position: sticky;
    top: 140px;
  }

  .about-value {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-5);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }

  .about-value__icon {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about-value__title {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-on-surface);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about-value p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .about-cta {
    background-color: var(--color-orange-dark);
    background-image: url('/images/patterns/tropical-pattern.png');
    background-size: 400px;
    background-repeat: repeat;
    color: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-cta__heading {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-cta__text {
    color: var(--color-outline-variant);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-cta .btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .about-content__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-7);
    }

    .about-values {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 639px) {
    .about-values {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
